column2: SELECT sp.ra,sp.dec,sp.z,sp.class, sp.psfmag_u-sp.extinction_u AS mag_u, sp.psfmag_g-sp.extinction_g AS mag_g, sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r AS mag_r, sp.psfmag_i-sp.extinction_i AS mag_i, sp.psfmag_z-sp.extinction_z AS mag_z, w.w1mpro AS w1, w.w2mpro AS w2,   w.w3mpro AS w3,   sp.zwarning, w.w4mpro AS w4 into mydb.MyTable_zwarningcolumn from SpecPhoto AS sp JOIN wise_xmatch AS xm ON sp.objid = xm.sdss_objid JOIN wise_allsky AS w ON xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr JOIN stellarMassPassivePort AS m ON sp.specobjid = m.specobjid WHERE    sp.psfmag_r-sp.extinction_r > #   AND sp.zWarning = #
